OL,3,CStillbirths at hospital to be reviewed
OL,4,Cafter report found issues in care
OL,6,FAll stillbirths at a Black Country
OL,7,Fhospital during 2025 are set to be
OL,8,Freviewed following a report which
OL,9,Ffound issues in the care of babies and
OL,10,Fmothers.
OL,12,FSandwell and West Birmingham NHS Trust
OL,13,Fwill be looking at all stillbirths
OL,14,Fwhich occurred last year at Midland
OL,15,FMetropolitan University Hospital.
OL,17,FThe review has been revealed in
OL,18,Fcorrespondence between campaigner Tom
OL,19,FHender and Health Secretary Wes
OL,20,FStreeting, seen by ITV News Central.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
