OL,3,CStillbirths at hospital to be reviewed
OL,4,Cafter report found issues in care
OL,6,FIt comes after a Care Quality
OL,7,FCommission (CQC) report in February
OL,8,F2026, which found issues in the care
OL,9,Fof some of the stillbirths at the
OL,10,FTrust. These issues were not
OL,11,Fhighlighted in the Trust's own data.
OL,13,FIn that report, the CQC reviewed 19
OL,14,Fstillbirths and late foetal losses
OL,15,Fbetween March and August 2025.
OL,17,FData from the Trust showed none of
OL,18,Fthem had "issues with care that was
OL,19,Flikely to have made the difference to
OL,20,Fthe outcome for the baby".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1776963956
OL,3,CStillbirths at hospital to be reviewed
OL,4,Cafter report found issues in care
OL,6,FHowever, issues highlighted in the CQC
OL,7,Freport included "growth restrictions
OL,8,Fdetected but serial scans not arranged
OL,9,Fand indication for gestational
OL,10,Fdiabetes testing but not offered".
OL,12,FITV News has seen a letter from Wes
OL,13,FStreeting which says that an external
OL,14,Freview is set to take place "intended
OL,15,Fto ensure that all internal reviews of
OL,16,Fstillbirth cases are of a consistent
OL,17,Fand high standard and that no issues
OL,18,Fwith care were missed".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1776963956
OL,3,CStillbirths at hospital to be reviewed
OL,4,Cafter report found issues in care
OL,6,FThe letter explains that contact is
OL,7,Fbeing made with all those families
OL,8,Fwhose cases are included in the review
OL,9,Fand says that the Trust is putting in
OL,10,Fplace support for the families should
OL,11,Fthey want it.
OL,13,FClaire Macdiarmid, director of
OL,14,Fmidwifery at the Trust, said: "As part
OL,15,Fof our commitment to continuous
OL,16,Fimprovement in maternity care, we are
OL,17,Flooking back at any stillbirths that
OL,18,Foccurred in 2025 to identify themes
OL,19,Fand learning.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1776963956
OL,3,CStillbirths at hospital to be reviewed
OL,4,Cafter report found issues in care
OL,6,F"We recognise how important it is that
OL,7,Ffamilies feel supported throughout
OL,8,Fthis process, and we will have support
OL,9,Favailable to help reduce the risk of
OL,10,Fre-traumatisation and to ensure
OL,11,Ffamilies are supported with
OL,12,Fcompassion, sensitivity, and
OL,13,Fconsistency.
OL,15,F"We will contact each family affected
OL,16,Fto provide them an opportunity to
OL,17,Fdecide if they wish to have their
OL,18,Fexperiences heard as part of the
OL,19,Freview.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1776963956
OL,3,CStillbirths at hospital to be reviewed
OL,4,Cafter report found issues in care
OL,6,F"We want to thank the families who
OL,7,Fhave already shared their experiences
OL,8,Fof stillbirth with us, which have
OL,9,Fhighlighted the need for improvements
OL,10,Fto be made, and we are committed to
OL,11,Fcontinuing to listen, learn and take
OL,12,Faction."
OL,14,FSupport and advice available for
OL,15,Fparents and families:
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/6
